"You must install ``php-smbclient`` version 0.8.0+. This should be "
"included in most Linux distributions. See `eduardok/libsmbclient-php "
"<https://github.com/eduardok/libsmbclient-php>`_ if your distribution "
"does not include it; this provides source archives and instructions how "
"to install binary packages."
